04:54.983 --> 05:04.577
the depressed economy of Texas and Houston in 
particular? We have several programs that are

05:05.755 --> 05:17.971
designed to stimulate economic redevelopment in 
low-moderate income areas, which is an area that

05:05.755 --> 05:17.971
encompasses roughly a third of the entire city. 
