05:20.073 --> 05:25.761
Community Development Block Grant. We have a 
small business revolving on fund program the

05:32.131 --> 05:48.330
small business owners who are doing business, who 
are located in one of our low-moderate income

05:32.131 --> 05:48.330
areas, they can, the way the program is presently 
structured, they can apply, business owners can

05:32.131 --> 05:48.330
apply for a tandem loan, which means we will make 
half the loan. The other half has to come from the

05:48.350 --> 05:50.012
bank. But we are in the process of amending that 
program because we found that banks are really not

05:57.562 --> 06:02.088
